description: K-Fast Holding AB is a SE-based company operating in Real Estate Management & Development industry. The company is headquartered in Hassleholm, Skane and currently employs 68 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2019-11-29. K-Fast Holding AB is a Sweden-based company engaged in the real estate industry. The firm focuses on acquiring, building and managing of properties. The firm serves customers in Sweden.
